# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AudiobookMaker local secrets and config — template.
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values.
# `.env` is gitignored; `.env.example` is tracked.
# Loaded automatically by scripts that read secrets (via python-dotenv).
# Frozen .exe builds do NOT read .env — those paths use os.environ only.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Hugging Face personal access token (read scope is enough).
# Used for:
#   - pyannote/speaker-diarization-3.1 gated model (voice-pack pipeline)
#   - Higher rate limits on large HF model downloads (VoxCPM2,
#     Chatterbox base, etc.). Unauthenticated downloads stall mid-stream
#     on ~4 GB weights.
# Generate at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens (read scope).
HF_TOKEN=
